column9: Continuation of suspended game from 2005-11-21 where Jiri Fischer (DET) suffered a cardiac arrest on the bench. Played full 60 minutes but game started with 1-0 Nashville lead.
Game suspended and completed on 2010-01-10 due to lighting problem.
Rescheduled to 2014-01-25 due to rescheduled 2014-01-22 game.
Continuation of suspended game from 2014-03-10 where Rich Peverley (DAL) suffered a cardiac event on the bench. Played full 60 minutes but game started with 1-0 Columbus lead.
